%% E030 - CrawlerWorker flow - F1-2 Pipeline CSJN
%% Source: docs/design/f1-2-crawler.md (E029)
flowchart TB
    Start([Receive CrawlerMessage]) --> ResolveDate[Resolve date range]
    ResolveDate --> Selenium[Selenium: navigate consulta.html, set dates, click Buscar]
    Selenium --> FetchPage[Fetch pagination page]
    FetchPage --> ValidateSchema[Validate response schema]
    ValidateSchema --> SchemaOK{Schema valid?}
    SchemaOK -->|No| LogDLQ[Log error, move to queue-crawler-dlq]
    LogDLQ --> EndFail([End - crawl failed])
    SchemaOK -->|Yes| Throttle[Wait ThrottlingDelayMs]
    Throttle --> Parse[Parse idAnalisis, Codigo per Record]
    Parse --> DocLoop{More documents?}
    DocLoop -->|No| MorePages{More pages?}
    MorePages -->|Yes| FetchPage
    MorePages -->|No| UpdateConfig[Update CrawlerConfigs]
    UpdateConfig --> EndOk([End - crawl completed])
    DocLoop -->|Yes| DownloadPDF[Download PDF]
    DownloadPDF --> RateLimit{429 or rate limit?}
    RateLimit -->|Yes| Retry{Retries left?}
    Retry -->|Yes| Backoff[Exponential backoff, retry]
    Backoff --> DownloadPDF
    Retry -->|No| LogDLQ
    RateLimit -->|No| ComputeHash[Compute ContentHash]
    ComputeHash --> ExistsHash{ContentHash in Rulings?}
    ExistsHash -->|Yes| DocLoop
    ExistsHash -->|No| UploadBlob[Upload PDF to Blob]
    UploadBlob --> Publish[Publish ParserMessage to queue-parser]
    Publish --> DocLoop
